caller_intent: Corbin is checking if his insurance policies (auto and homeowners) are still the best option, particularly after a coverage increase on his homeowners policy, and wants to review the auto rate for potential discounts.
resolution_steps: Arlo explains the homeowners coverage increase from $2,800 to $3,720 due to roof age.
Arlo proposes checking the auto rate tomorrow to see if a 14% discount is possible.
Arlo schedules a follow-up call for the next day (Friday) to review policies and finalize by the weekend.
Arlo assures Corbin he will return calls if unavailable.
knowledge_required: Auto insurance rate calculations and discounts
summary: Corbin discusses his upcoming insurance renewal with Arlo, who explains a homeowners coverage increase and plans to check the auto rate for potential discounts. They agree to finalize policies by the weekend after a follow-up call.
